window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Inspired by classic science fiction such as </b><b><i>Contact</i></b><b> by Carl Sagan and the film </b><b><i>Explorers</i></b><b>, </b><b><i>Reckless Faith</i></b><b> is a fascinating slow burn that ignites into a bonfire by the second book in the series.</b></p> <p>If you had the chance to construct a spacecraft using alien technology, would you embark on the project yourself or turn it over to the government? <i>Reckless Faith</i> is a story about three friends who choose to pursue this seemingly impossible task, no matter what the cost. When an alien device appears in the woods of northern New Hampshire, John, Ray, and Arianna are the first ones to find it, and soon realize it is offering them a unique opportunity.</p> <p><b>Will they be able to accomplish it alone?</b></p>"; 
